%F A339334 T(n,k) = A339333(n,k) for all k when 1 <= n <= 7 or n = 10.
%F A339334 T(n,k) = A339333(n,k) for all n when k = 1 or k = 2.
%F A339334 T(n,k) >= A339333(n,k).
